            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the mum-guilt loop. The script targets the guilt that arrives after a hard parenting moment — a child's disappointment, a snap that went too long, another mother's comment that landed too hard, or the day's accumulated sense of having done it all wrong."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "text": "Even though I feel like I'm getting this wrong, I deeply and completely accept myself." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "text": "Even though the guilt is loud today, I deeply and completely accept myself." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "text": "Even though I'm tired and I snapped and I wish I hadn't, I deeply and completely accept myself." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I'm convinced I'm doing this wrong." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " Whatever I choose feels like the wrong choice." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " The guilt arrived again today." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I'm scared of getting it wrong in the ways that matter." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I carry this guilt into every decision." }
