      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's earlier Thought Field Therapy. The eight-point sequence follows Craig's standard shorthand. The mum-guilt theme and the specific script are original to the homemade.education library."
